SELECT jobs.job_id, jobs.job_type, jobs.payload
                            FROM jobs, rats
                            WHERE rats.public_key = ?
                                AND rats.rat_id = jobs.rat_id
                                AND jobs.started = false
                            ORDER BY job_id ASC
                            LIMIT 1
